    "en": {
      "title": "President goes to Kataragama",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe is scheduled to visit Monaragala and Kataragama this coming weekend.",
        "Accordingly, the President is scheduled to visit Monaragala on the 27th to meet the Monaragala District Development Council at the Monaragala Library auditorium.",
        "After that, on the 28th, the President is scheduled to visit Kataragama Kirivehera and Temple, Vadasiti Kanda Viharaya, Tissamaharama Viharaya."
      ],
